{
  "stem": "2118.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Or very few people out of the whole school, if I know, if I remember right-- two children got a scholarship to go what they called the-- a gymnasium, which here would be a high school, or a little better than high school.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now going back to my childhood, I-- I had lots of friends.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were religious, but not too religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We observed all the holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Saturday was Saturday.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But we were not that-- well, maybe my father-- but the children-- we did go to a movie.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We would take the streetcar to get out of town in summer to go to-- to a lake or something like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we had-- we were not-- we were considered already advanced in-- in religion, or maybe-- I wouldn't say religion.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Well, religion was religion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Except, we would do certain things which the real orthodox or ultra orthodox would frown at, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They would never do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We owned a-- a big building in partnership with-- with a uncle and another person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were eight in the family included.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Every day, to dinner, the whole family was there, eight of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And my oldest brother was independent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He had, well, I should-- I should go back first to my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My father was what you would call here a mechanic, or a general mechanic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We had a little shop in the same building we lived in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he would fix things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "In other words, he would fix general things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Somebody needed a lock fixed, he would fix it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Somebody locked himself out, they would call him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He will open it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
